<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>maggot.io</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/main.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.6.2/css/font-awesome.min.css'/>
  </head>
  <body>
    
    <div class="row">

    	<div class="column small-3" id="sidebar">
    		<div class="logo">
    			<i class="fa fa-bug"></i> maggot.io
			</div>

    	</div>

    	<div class="column small-9" id="contents">
    		<div class="content-header">
    			Getting Started
    		</div>

    		<div class="row">
    			<div class="column small-12">
	    			<p>
		    			Welcome! Looks like it's your first time using <strong>maggot.io</strong>.
					</p>
		    		<p>
		    			<strong>maggot.io</strong> requires a MongoDB database to work. Before you continue, you'll need to install a MongoDB database on this computer or somewhere you have network access to.
					</p>
					<p>
						If you have <code>brew</code>, you can install <strong>MongoDB</strong> with the following command:

						<code>brew install mongodb</code>
					</p>
					<p>
						Or click <strong>Get MongoDB</strong> below to download the installer.
					</p>

					<p>
						<a href="https://www.mongodb.com/download-center" target="_blank">
							<button class="button">
								<i class="fa fa-cloud-download"></i> Get MongoDB
							</button>
						</a>

						<button class="button hollow">
							<i class="fa fa-check"></i> I already have MondoDB
						</button>
					</p>

				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<footer class="row align-justify">
		<div class="column">
			Made with <i class="fa fa-heart"></i> by Dan Johnson
		</div>
		<div class="column shrink">
			<a href="#">
				<i class="fa fa-github"></i> GitHub</a>
		</div>
	</footer>


  </body>
</html>
